#define GREETINGS ["You are such a tiny, shivering spark, %s. Do you not fear the frost?","How did you even find this place, %s? You are barely worth the effort of a freeze.","I can smell the heat radiating off you. It’s pathetic. Fade away, %s.","A snack. You are nothing more than a fragile, warm snack, %s.","Do not bother approaching, %s. My cold is absolute, and you are far too soft.","I can hear your heart hammering in your chest, %s. It’s drumming with such trivial fear.","You tremble in my presence, %s. And well you should—the blizzard is coming.","Fragile. That is the only word for you, %s. Don't break before we even begin.","Your pulse is slow, %s. Are you already preparing for the deep freeze?","Your energy is inconsequential, %s. Leave before I decide to preserve you in ice.","You have a spark, %s, but it is nothing compared to the eternal hunger of the frost.","Step carefully, %s. You are walking on ice that could swallow you whole.","I see you, %s. Do not mistake my observation for interest.","Are you looking to be part of the landscape, %s? Because that is all you are to me.","You are trying so hard to be significant, %s. It is truly adorable.","Finally, a mind that isn't completely silent, %s. Speak quickly before you lose your heat.","You carry a heavy burden, %s. I can feel the weight of it, even beneath the ice.","There is a strange order in your chaotic movements, %s. I find that... tolerable.","Do you enjoy this level of existence, %s? It seems so dangerously limited.","Stay within your boundaries, %s, and you may endure for a little while longer.","Your potential is vibrant, %s. A pity it will be buried beneath so much winter.","I can feel the power you withhold, %s. Why hide it from the cold?","Your energy resonates with mine, %s. It is... unexpected and quite sharp.","You have strength, %s. Let us see if it is enough to survive my sub-zero embrace.","You are interesting, %s. I might let you watch as I flash-freeze the world.","Such raw power in one so finite, %s. I am genuinely intrigued by your resistance.","You hold back the tide of my frost, %s. I can feel the intensity of your spirit cracking.","A worthy vessel, %s. If only you knew what true, absolute zero felt like.","Your strength is a beacon, %s. It calls to my hunger.","Do not fear, %s. I have space in my arctic tomb for one like you.","At last, a soul that doesn't shatter when I look into the deep freeze. Welcome, %s.","You possess a magnitude that borders on the divine, %s. I have been waiting for a peer.","Your power... it is almost enough to rival the bite of the living frost, %s.","Together, %s, we could rewrite the laws of the universe in ice.","I recognize a force of nature when I see one. Stand with me, %s, and we shall be the eternal winter."]

#define WrestleWin ["A frozen snack. You were barely a crunch, %s.","The cold claims you, %s. Go into the deep freeze, forever.","Did you feel that? The moment your blood turned to slush? You're done, %s.","Ice preserves... and you, %s, shall be a statue of your own failure.","Too warm. You were far too warm to be any fun, %s.","Your warmth was fading before we even began, %s. Pathetic.","I'll leave you as a sculpture in the snow, %s. A monument to my hunger.","You struggled like a trapped bird, %s. It was almost... endearing.","Freeze solid, %s. The world moves on without your shivering.","You were a nuisance, %s. Now, you’re just part of the landscape.","You held the frost for a moment, %s. A rare achievement for a mortal.","The cold is absolute, %s. You were just a temporary obstruction.","Still moving? Let me fix that. Hibernate, %s.","Your pulse slowed significantly, %s. The end is so very... chilling.","You had a bit of bite, %s. Too bad the Symbiote has a stronger one.","You put up a flurry, %s, but the blizzard always wins.","A respectable dance, %s. But you're brittle. I could hear you cracking.","The temperature drops when I'm around, %s. Don't act surprised.","You were almost a challenge. Almost enough to warm me up, %s.","Rest now, %s. The eternal winter is quite peaceful.","Your heat was... vibrant. I’ll savor that, %s.","You forced the frost to bite back, %s. I admire that about you.","A glorious fight! You are the first in a long time to make me shiver, %s.","You had power, %s. It’s a shame to bury it beneath so much ice.","You are worthy of the tomb, %s. Sleep in the arctic silence.","You are strong, %s! My tendrils ache from the resistance! A wonderful hunt!","A titan of temperature! I almost enjoyed the struggle, %s.","My host is satisfied. You were a worthy test of our sub-zero potential, %s.","You crack like glacier ice, %s. Strong, but ultimately, you break.","We are the winter that never ends, %s. You were just a brief storm.","Magnificent! You and I—we are the absolute zero of the universe, %s!","I have not felt such a battle since the stars were young! You are an elite prize, %s!","You are the storm I’ve been waiting to swallow, %s. Simply exquisite.","A legend falls to the frost. The history books will be written in ice, %s.","You are more than a foe; you are a legacy. I will keep you frozen in my memory, %s."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["A fluke! The cold will return, %s! I am inevitable!","Impossible... how can someone so tepid defeat the living frost?","You got lucky, %s. Do not think this warmth will last.","My host is weak... this isn't over, %s!","I retreat to the depths! You have only delayed the frost, %s!","How? I am the glacial end! You are nothing, %s!","You’ve disrupted the cycle... it won't be so easy next time, %s.","You cannot kill the cold, %s! I will return with a vengeance!","You think you’ve won? You’ve only pushed me into the dark, %s.","My defeat is a calculation I missed... I will adjust, %s.","The temperature is rising... I am retreating to recalibrate, %s.","You caught me off guard, %s. Victory is a fleeting, warm dream for you.","The frost is patient, %s. I will wait for your heat to fail.","You are a strange variable, %s. I will remember this anomaly.","My tendrils are scorched... this isn't finished, %s!","This is not the end. The thaw is temporary, %s. The ice always returns.","You are an anomaly I will correct, %s. Mark my words.","Do not celebrate, %s. My hunger is vast, and I will be back.","You hold the ground today, %s. Tomorrow, the world will freeze.","Your victory is a disturbance in my design, %s. I will smooth it over.","You possess a heat I did not anticipate, %s. Truly fascinating.","I yield the field today, %s. Do not think I lack the power to win.","You are a nuisance, %s. I shall eliminate that nuisance permanently.","So, this is the warmth you hide? It will not save you for long, %s.","I will return with a strategy tailored to your melting point, %s.","This defeat is a strategic necessity. I retreat, but the ice never sleeps, %s.","You have fought well, %s. It is a pity you are destined to be frozen.","Critical damage sustained. You have won this round, but the blizzard is coming, %s.","You are a formidable variable, %s. I shall incorporate you into my next hunt.","Victory today, frost tomorrow. We shall see how long your heat lasts, %s.","Unbelievable. To be bested... you have proven to be a dangerous, burning star, %s.","You are the first to truly force my withdrawal in ages, %s. I am... intrigued.","My icy essence is overloaded. You are indeed a peer in power, %s.","I concede this battle, %s. You have earned the right to face the storm.","A pyrrhic victory for you, %s. Next time, I will not be so gracious."]
